Class Student

java.lang.Object
at.mci.assigment_1.Student
public class Student extends Object
Represents a student with details such as name, student ID, gender, group, and proficiency in Java. The class keeps track of the number of student instances created. Fields:
  • name: The name of the student.
  • group: The group that the student is part of.
  • proficiencyInJava: The student's proficiency level in Java.
  • studentID: The unique identifier for the student.
  • gender: The gender of the student.
  • numberOfStundents: The amount of all students as static variable
  • grades: A list for all the grades a student has achieved (as int since MCI uses int
Author:
Clemens Wanker
